      <h2 class="scroll-reveal">The Journey</h2>
      <p class="scroll-reveal delay-1">Every great fragrance starts with a story. Here's ours.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-timeline">
      <div class="about-timeline-item">
        <div class="about-timeline-text scroll-reveal-left">
          <h3>The Beginning</h3>
          <h4>A Passion Ignited</h4>
          <p>SHMNI was born from a simple belief: luxury fragrances should be accessible to everyone. What started as a personal obsession with scent profiles and rare ingredients evolved into a brand with a mission — to craft perfumes that tell stories.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-timeline-visual scroll-reveal-right">🌿</div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-timeline-item">
        <div class="about-timeline-text scroll-reveal-right">
          <h3>The Craft</h3>
          <h4>Mastering the Art</h4>
          <p>We studied the greatest perfume houses in the world and partnered with master perfumers to create compositions that rival luxury brands at a fraction of the cost. Every formula is tested over 100 times before we consider it worthy of the SHMNI name.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-timeline-visual scroll-reveal-left">🧪</div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-timeline-item">
        <div class="about-timeline-text scroll-reveal-left">
          <h3>The Experience</h3>
          <h4>Beyond the Bottle</h4>
          <p>A fragrance is more than a scent — it's confidence, memory, and identity. We designed every touchpoint of the SHMNI experience, from our AI-powered Scent Quiz to our luxurious unboxing, to make you feel extraordinary.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-timeline-visual scroll-reveal-right">✨</div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-timeline-item">
        <div class="about-timeline-text scroll-reveal-right">
          <h3>The Future</h3>
          <h4>Always Evolving</h4>
          <p>We're constantly pushing boundaries — experimenting with rare ingredients, sustainable practices, and innovative ways to help you discover your perfect scent. The best is yet to come.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-timeline-visual scroll-reveal-left">🚀</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ═══ QUOTE ═══ -->
  <div class="about-quote">
    <blockquote class="scroll-reveal">"Scent is the most powerful form of self-expression. It speaks before you do, lingers after you leave, and becomes the invisible signature of who you are."</blockquote>
    <cite class="scroll-reveal delay-1">— SHMNI</cite>
  </div>

  <!-- ═══ VALUES ═══ -->
  <div class="about-values">
    <div class="about-values-inner">
      <div class="about-values-header">
        <h2 class="scroll-reveal">What We Stand For</h2>
        <p class="scroll-reveal delay-1">The pillars that define everything we create</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-values-grid">
        <div class="about-value-card scroll-reveal">
          <div class="about-value-icon">💎</div>
          <h3>Uncompromising Quality</h3>
          <p>We source only the finest ingredients from around the world. No shortcuts, no compromises — ever.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-value-card scroll-reveal delay-1">
          <div class="about-value-icon">🌍</div>
